            <h5 class="title"> Explore Zoolirante Through Our Interactive Map</h5>
            <p>
                Our interactive map brings the zoo to online,
                Click on the animals to uncover their stories, and plan your perfect visit with ease.
                Discover fascinating facts, photos, and highlights as you navigate the zoo right from your screen.
            </p>

        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="section-map">

        <div class="map-wrap">
            <a class="pin" href="/AnimalList/Details/4" style="top: 30%; left: 20%; background: rgba(255, 128, 0, .9);">Pandas</a>
            <a class="pin" href="/AnimalList/Details/1" style="top: 56%; left: 68%; background: rgba(255, 128, 0, .9);">Lions</a>
            <a class="pin" href="/AnimalList/Details/3" style="top: 76%;left: 30%;background: rgba(255, 128, 0, .9);">Giraffes</a>
            <a class="pin" href="/AnimalList/Details/5" style="top: 40%; left: 50%; background: rgba(255, 128, 0, .9);">Elephants</a>
            <a class="pin" href="/AnimalList/Details/5" style="top: 95%;left: 64%;background: rgba(255, 128, 0, .9);">Zebras</a>
            <a class="pin" href="/AnimalList/Details/12" style="top: 20%; left: 80%; background: rgba(255, 128, 0, .9);">Polar Bears</a>

        </div>


    </div>

</section>

